" <div class=\"graphic\">",
"  <div class=\"figure\" style=\"width: 470px\">",
"   <div class=\"ttl\">",
"    Nonpupil-sparing third nerve palsy",
"   </div>",
"   <div class=\"cntnt\" style=\"width: 432px; height: 207px; background-image: url(data:image/jpeg;base64,);\">",
"   </div>",
"   <div class=\"lgnd\">",
"    Right mydriasis in a patient with a right third nerve palsy secondary to a posterior communicating aneurysm. The patient also had a mild ptosis and complained of diplopia with reduced adduction, elevation, and depression of the right eye. Abduction and intorsion were normal in the right eye.",
