"   <div class=\"cntnt\" style=\"width: 256px; height: 400px; background-image: url(data:image/jpeg;base64,);\">",
"   </div>",
"   <div class=\"lgnd\">",
"    The essential lesion is a small, erythematous, nondescript papule.",
"    <div class=\"footnotes\">",
"    </div>",
